		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName><sic>Trenten</sic> N. J</placeName> <date>9 Augt.&#47;66</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isc Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philada.</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I have received your<lb/> favor of <date>6th</date> inst. and was pained<lb/> to learn that my son <persName>Abraham</persName> had<lb/> imposed upon yr. kindness.  He is<lb/> unfortunately not right in his mind<lb/> and still not sufficiently so to war&#61;<lb/>&#45;rant his confinement in an asylum.<lb/>  He has occasioned his mother &#38;<lb/> myself great unhappiness.  Altho&#39;<lb/> I appreciate your motive in assisting<lb/> him I regret you did so&#44; because<lb/> there was no necessity for his absence<lb/> from home&#59; &#45;I send you enclosed<lb/> &#36;5. in paymt. of what you were kind<lb/> enough to advance him.  He is still<lb/> absent&#44; &#38; should he apply to you<lb/> again I hope you will refuse him.</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>and if you happen to see him lecture<lb/> him as severely as you can.&#8212;.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">With best <add>respects</add> from <persName>Mrs Haart<add>&#63;</add></persName> &#38; my family I am</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Yours very resfuly</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">Dd. Haart</persName></p>
		</body>
